# Project documentation

## Before implementing

Read **docs/README.md** and **docs/CURRENT_STATE.md**. For planned features, read the matching spec in **docs/specs/**.

Do not treat conversation history as source of truth.

## After shipping (required)

Update repo docs in the **same commit** as code changes:

1. **docs/CURRENT_STATE.md** — always (routes, env vars, file paths, limitations)
2. **docs/ROADMAP.md** — if a roadmap item is done
3. **docs/specs/*.md** — check off completed phases; resolve open questions
4. **docs/PRODUCT.md** — only if user-facing flows or scope changed
5. **docs/ARCHITECTURE.md** — only if new subsystem or data model pattern
6. **apps/web/.env.example** — if new env vars

Full matrix: **AGENTS.md** → Documentation maintenance.

## Build order

Competitions picker → Match ingest → unit-stake points → group stats (docs/ROADMAP.md).
